" Use <C-X><C-C><C-V> to cut/copy/paste {{{
vnoremap <C-X> "+x
vnoremap <C-C> "+y
map <C-V> "+gP
cmap <C-V> <C-R>+
exe 'inoremap <script> <C-V>' paste#paste_cmd['i']
exe 'vnoremap <script> <C-V>' paste#paste_cmd['v']
noremap <C-Q> <C-V>
"}}}

" Use <C-S> to save {{{
nmap <C-S> :update<CR>
imap <C-S> <C-O>:update<CR>
"}}}

